### senario 2 (left picture) : nums[mid] > nums[left]
if (target >= nums[left] && target < nums[mid]):  calls Binary search
else left = mid + 1;
### senario 3 (right picture) : nums[mid] <= nums[left]
if (target > nums[mid] && target <= nums[right]):  calls Binary search
else right = mid - 1;
