solutions.content:
Problem statement says we have to create deep copy of the graph (**Deep Copy : creating completely new graph that is similar to original graph but has no connection with it which means it is not using the node used in original graph** )
Node class has two members:
1. value of node
2. List containing address of nodes adjacent to current node 

Initially Node* node pointer is pointing to the node with val =1
**Approach:** I will be
* Using BFS queue.
* Using hashmap to keep track of visited nodes 
    * I will be storing address of original node with is pointing to its copy node address  like:
    *  address(1) Ori---> address(1) new.copy

 **Pseudo code**  
1.  start with given source node creates its copy add its original address + new address into hashmap & push original address  into queue .
    ***Why Original?***
	Because till now we only created copy of node but its adjacent nodes are not described till now.
	what we will do is?
	* we will pop node at front of queue
	* check for its neighbors 
	*if neighbours is not already existent in map create its copy and put its address in the new node neigbours vector.
	*if existent then 
	put its address in the new node neigbours vector.



2.  Now ,Turn to its adjacent nodes 
       * if adjacent node is not visited then
            * create its copy with val same as original adjacent node 
            * Push original adjacent node address into queue
            * m[original address of adjacent]--> m[new address of adjacent]
            * store address of new adjacent node address into the neighbors vector of the new address of front node .
            ![image](https://assets.leetcode.com/users/images/888b1442-752c-4137-af85-8f9431223cb2_1645625768.9942315.jpeg)


		* else i.e. is already visited ,then 
		    * Simply   store address adready adjacent node  into the neighbors vector of the new address of front node . 

**Dry Run**

![image](https://assets.leetcode.com/users/images/d7a8c152-4210-41aa-a035-82c3c369772f_1645626773.853613.jpeg)
![image](https://assets.leetcode.com/users/images/e1265e44-a47d-40f9-8f8b-5c7a9366feed_1645626773.883312.jpeg)


